{"lemma":"بَكْرُ","slug":"بَكْرُ","root":"ب.ك.ر","root_slug":"ب-ك-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ك-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَكْرُ","root":"بكر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3064","n3065","n3067","n3068","n3069","n3070","n3072"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be early"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come early","examples":[{"text":"بَكَرَ إِلَيْهِ قَبْلَ أَنْ يُغادِرَ بَيْتَهُ."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to get up early"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be early"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to come early"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to get up early"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to early or prematurely"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Bakr","examples":[{"text":"أبو بكر، بو بكر","english":"The father of Bakr"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"firstborn child"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"male or female virgin, celibate","examples":[{"text":"فَجَعَلْنَاهُنَّ أَبْكَارًا","english":"And [we] made them virgins"},{"text":"يَا مَرْيَمُ الْبِكْرُ فُقْتِ الشَّمْسَ وَالْقَمَرَ وَكُلَّ نَجْمٍ بِأَفْلَاكِ السَّمَاءِ سَرَى","english":"O Virgin Mary, ye surpassed the sun and the moon and all the stars that orbited the heavenly spheres by night."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of بُكْرَة (bukra)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew בְּכוֹר (bəḵōr, “firstborn”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3064","headword_ar":"بَكَرَ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"both [properly] relate to the beginning of the day: (AZ, Msb:) the former of these verbs, (T, S, A,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bukuwrN","text_ar":"بُكُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r","text_ar":"بكّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabokiyrN","text_ar":"تَبْكِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abtkr","text_ar":"ابتكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAkr","text_ar":"باكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) all signify the same; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a traveller, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went forth early in the morning, in the first part of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the time of the prayer of daybreak and sunrise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja fiY Albukorapi","text_ar":"خَرَجَ فِى البُكْرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, A:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibokaArN","text_ar":"اـِبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he entered upon that time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakura","text_ar":"بَكُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"nor"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakira","text_ar":"بَكِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r","text_ar":"بكّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]. (S.) ―         -b2-  You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakara A_ilayohi","text_ar":"بَكَرَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r","text_ar":"بكّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abtkr","text_ar":"ابتكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAkrhu","text_ar":"باكرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAhu bukorapN","text_ar":"اَتَاهُ بُكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, early in the morning, in the first part of the day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the time of the prayer of daybreak and sunrise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did it at that time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakara","text_ar":"بَكَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi","text_ar":"فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"following may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he occupied himself at that time in doing it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b3-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakara A_ilayohi","text_ar":"بَكَرَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor. and inf. n. as above; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakira Alyh","text_ar":"بَكِرَ اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (ISd, K; * [but see a remark respecting this verb above;]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyh","text_ar":"اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bkr","text_ar":"بكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyh","text_ar":"اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Elyh","text_ar":"عليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkrhu","text_ar":"ابكرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAkrhu","text_ar":"باكرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) signify also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betook himself early"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"at any time, (S, Msb, K, TA,) morning or evening. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakarotu EalaY AlHaAjapi","text_ar":"بَكَرْتُ عَلَى الحَاجَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I hastened to do,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attain, the thing needed"},{"kind":"text","text":"], inf. n. as above: and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Alwirodi","text_ar":"عَلَى الوِرْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokarotu","text_ar":"اَبْكَرْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I hastened to come to water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (AZ, S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwiroda","text_ar":"الوِرْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgadaA='a","text_ar":"الغَدَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, S, TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened to come to water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take the morning-meal."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Lebeed says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"baAkarotu jaAjatahaA Ald~ajaAja bisuHorapK"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I hastened to be before"},{"kind":"text","text":"the crowing of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cock, at the close of night, in obtaining what was wanted"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, of wine,] by me: (TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAjthA","text_ar":"حاجتها"},{"kind":"text","text":"being for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjatiY A_ilayohaA","text_ar":"حَاجَتِى اـِلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxamori","text_ar":"الخَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (EM p. 170: but the first word is there written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdarotu","text_ar":"بَادَرْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See also 2, below.] ―         -b4-  [It is also said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bkr","text_ar":"بكر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakira","text_ar":"بَكِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bkr","text_ar":"بكر"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakarN","text_ar":"بَكَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possessed the quality of applying himself early,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of hastening;"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna SaAHiba bukuwrK","text_ar":"كَانَ صَاحِبَ بُكُورٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) [But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakurN","text_ar":"بَكُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["AZ","Msb","T","S","A","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n3065","headword_ar":"بكّر","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tabokiyrN","text_ar":"تَبْكِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in three places: and see 8. You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r A_ilaY AljumoEapi","text_ar":"بكّر اـِلَى الجُمْعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went forth to the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prayers of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Friday at the commencement of the time thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r","text_ar":"بكّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], inf. n. as above, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to prayer at the commencement of its time."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r biAlS~alaApi","text_ar":"بكّر بِالصَّلَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He performed the prayer at the commencement of its time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, Msb, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was regardful of it, and performed it early."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bak~iruwA biSalaApi Almagoribi","text_ar":"بَكِّرُوا بِصَلَاةِ المَغْرِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Perform ye"},{"kind":"page_break","n":240},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the prayer of sunset at the setting of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sun's"},{"kind":"text","text":"] disc. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bak~arati Aln~axolapu biHamolihaA","text_ar":"بَكَّرَتِ النَّخْلَةُ بِحَمْلِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The palmtree was early with its fruit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, before; preceded; had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took, precedence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqad~ama","text_ar":"تَقَدَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkr","text_ar":"ابكر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbk~r","text_ar":"تبكّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bak~arotu fiY","text_ar":"بَكَّرْتُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, before,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqad~amotu","text_ar":"تَقَدَّمْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IJ, IB, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r EalaY A^aSoHaAbihi","text_ar":"بكّر عَلَى اَصْحَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, before his companions; preceded them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took, precedence of them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~rhu EalaY","text_ar":"بكّرهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHaAbihi","text_ar":"اَصْحَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalahu yubak~iru Ealayohimo","text_ar":"جَعَلَهُ يُبَكِّرُ عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"become,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go, before his companions; to precede them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take, precedence of them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohimo","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abkrhu","text_ar":"ابكرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  See also 4. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bk~r AlfaAkihapa","text_ar":"بكّر الفَاكِهَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8."}],"source_refs":["A","Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n3067","headword_ar":"بَكْرٌ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bukorN","text_ar":"بُكْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) but this latter is hardly to be found in any of the lexicons, (MF,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikorN","text_ar":"بِكْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A youthful he-camel; one in a state of youthful vigour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) and also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorN","text_ar":"بَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorN","text_ar":"بَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a camel, corresponds to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatFY","text_ar":"فَتًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a human being; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorapN","text_ar":"بَكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fataApN","text_ar":"فَتَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaluwSN","text_ar":"قَلُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAriyapN","text_ar":"جَارِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEiyrN","text_ar":"بَعِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inosaAnN","text_ar":"اـِنْسَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalN","text_ar":"جَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroA^apN","text_ar":"مَرْاَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AO, S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one, of a she-camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) thus indefinitely explained: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel in his sixth year"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniY~N","text_ar":"ثَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") [and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he becomes a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aE","text_ar":"جَذَع"},{"kind":"text","text":": [but it seems that the reverse must be meant; for a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j*E","text_ar":"جذع"},{"kind":"text","text":", of camels, is one in his fifth year:] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel in his second year"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he enters his sixth year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel in his second year,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has entered his third year,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has completed his second year and entered his third year;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibonu labuwnK","text_ar":"اِبْنُ لَبُونٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel that has just entered upon his fourth year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel in his fifth year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, Az:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a camel that has not entered his ninth year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and sometimes it is metaphorically applied to a human being; [meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorapN","text_ar":"بَكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the pl. (of pauc., S) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokurN","text_ar":"اَبْكُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ubayokiruwna","text_ar":"اُبَيْكِرُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs as pl. of the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokurN","text_ar":"اَبْكُرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) and (pl. of mult., S, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikaArN","text_ar":"بِكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"firaAxN","text_ar":"فِرَاخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroxN","text_ar":"فَرْخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) or this is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorapN","text_ar":"بَكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) and there are other pls. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorN","text_ar":"بَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bukoraAnN","text_ar":"بُكْرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikaArapN","text_ar":"بِكَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and [quasi-pl. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakaArapN","text_ar":"بَكَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) Hence the well-known prov., (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadaqaniY sin~a bakorihi","text_ar":"صَدَقَنِى سِنَّ بَكْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sin~u bakorihi","text_ar":"سِنُّ بَكْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hath told me what is in his mind, and what his ribs infold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a saying originating from the following fact: a man bargained with another for a youthful camel ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakor","text_ar":"بَكْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and said, “ What is his age ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sin~uhu","text_ar":"سِنُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")? ” the other answered, “ He is in his ninth year: ” then the young camel took fright and ran away: whereupon his owner said to him,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hidaEo hidaEo","text_ar":"هِدَعْ هِدَعْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and this is an expression by which are quieted young ones, (K,) of the camel; (TA;) so when the purchaser heard it, he said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SdqnY sn~ bkrh","text_ar":"صدقنى سنّ بكره"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hath told me truly the age,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as to the age, of his youthful camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the age of his youthful camel has spoken truly to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: if"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sn~","text_ar":"سنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the accus. case, the meaning [of the verb] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ear~afaniY","text_ar":"عَرَّفَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sn~","text_ar":"سنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the accus. case as a second objective complement; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabara sin~i","text_ar":"خَبَرَ سِنِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is meant; [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabara","text_ar":"خَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY sin~i","text_ar":"فِى سِنِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the prefixed noun ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabara","text_ar":"خَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or the proposition ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY","text_ar":"فِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] being suppressed [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sn~","text_ar":"سنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being therefore in the accus. case]: but if"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sn~","text_ar":"سنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the nom. case, veracity is attributed to the [animal's] age, by an amplification: (K:) or, as some say, the buyer said to the owner of the camel, “ How many years has he? ” and he told him; and he looked at the teeth of the camel, and found him to be as he had said; whereupon he said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SdqnY sin~u bkrh","text_ar":"صدقنى سِنُّ بكره"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 95.)"}],"source_refs":["K","MF","ISd","TA","AO","S","IAar","Az","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n3068","headword_ar":"بُكْرٌ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorN","text_ar":"بَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3069","headword_ar":"بِكْرٌ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A virgin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man who has not yet drawn near to a woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vay~ibN","text_ar":"ثَيِّبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"applied to a man as well as to a female:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaArN","text_ar":"اَبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pearl unpierced."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF.) And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bow when one first shoots with it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloud abounding with water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) likened to a virgin, because her blood is more than that of her who is not a virgin: and the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN bikorN","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ بِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes used. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naArN bikorN","text_ar":"نَارٌ بِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fire not lighted from another fire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, A.) ―         -b3-  Also She"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has not yet brought forth offspring:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth:) and a cow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has not yet conceived:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or a heifer (K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has not yet conceived:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and a woman, (S, K,) and a she-camel, (As, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has brought forth but once:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaArN","text_ar":"اَبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikaArN","text_ar":"بِكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or a she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in her first state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 340.) ―         -b4-  And [hence,] (tropical:)  A grape-vine"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has produced fruit but once:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaArN","text_ar":"اَبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) ―         -b5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorN","text_ar":"بَكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (ISd, TA.) And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaAru AlA^awolaAdi","text_ar":"اَبْكَارُ الاَوْلَادِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Young children."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaAru Aln~aHoli","text_ar":"اَبْكَارُ النَّحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Young bees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Whence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Easalu A^abokaArK","text_ar":"عَسَلُ اَبْكَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Honey produced by young bees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or this means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honey of which the preparation has been superintended by virgin-girls."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * TA.) ―         -b6-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first-born of his,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her, mother"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and father;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K;) applied alike to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and sometimes to that which is not the offspring of human beings; (TA;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first-born"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels; (S;) and of a serpent: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abokaArN","text_ar":"اَبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA bikoru A^abawayohi","text_ar":"هٰذَا بِكْرُ اَبَوَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is the first-born of his parents."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ad~u Aln~aAsi bikorN A@bonu bikorayoni","text_ar":"اَشَدُّ النَّاسِ بِكْرٌ ا@بْنُ بِكْرَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikoru bikorayoni","text_ar":"بِكْرُ بِكْرَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The strongest of men is the first-born of a man and woman each a first-born"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAkuwrapN","text_ar":"بَاكُورَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action that has not been preceded by its like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA h`*aA AlA^amoru minoka bikorFA wa laA vaniyFA","text_ar":"مَا هٰذَا الاَمْرُ مِنْكَ بِكْرًا وَ لَا ثَنِيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, is not thy first nor thy second."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjapN bikorN","text_ar":"حَاجَةٌ بِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"needful thing, recently sought to be accomplished"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is the first in being referred to him of whom its accomplishment is sought."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobapN","text_ar":"ضَرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bikorN","text_ar":"بِكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cutting blow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stroke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that kills"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at once,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not requiring to be struck a second time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarabaAtN A^abokaArN","text_ar":"ضَرَبَاتٌ اَبْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; occurring in a trad., in which it is said that such were the blows of 'Alee; (S, TA;) but in that trad., as some recite it, the latter word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubotakiraAtN","text_ar":"مُبْتَكِرَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","K","TA","AHeyth","S","As","A","M"]},{"entry_id":"n3070","headword_ar":"بَكَرٌ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bukorapN","text_ar":"بُكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bakorapN","text_ar":"بَكْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"page_break","n":241}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3072","headword_ar":"بَكِرٌ","root":"bkr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next precedes."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}